Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:13.23,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Angels planning disguised with devil's faces
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:20.24,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Children cling on to their very last coins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.20,op-en,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Destruction and regeneration
